  past "no" here, okay?

14:51.539 --> 14:53.841
i'm afraid to say.

14:53.841 --> 14:56.093
well, you're gonna
have to get over that.

14:56.093 --> 14:59.764
'cause i got him killed,
and if more is gonna happen--

14:59.764 --> 15:02.967
- you got kwasi killed?
- yes.

15:02.967 --> 15:06.387
tell us how you think
you got him killed.

15:06.387 --> 15:10.391
i had found some drugs
in my building.

15:10.391 --> 15:13.778
they were hidden
in a boom box
under the landing,

15:13.778 --> 15:18.115
