'cause of the storage area.

15:48.229 --> 15:50.932
what was his name?
he didn't say.

15:50.932 --> 15:53.234
he's the guy that was in the car
with you and kwasi?
yeah.

15:53.234 --> 15:57.855
how'd kwasi get into it?
i had went to him,
'cause i was afraid.

15:57.855 --> 16:02.410
i was supposed to meet him
today at fourth and "b."

16:02.410 --> 16:05.162
wait a minute.
this is prince, the guy
who wanted his drugs back?

16:05.162 --> 16:07.832
or either he was
gonna kill me.

16:07.832 --> 16:12.003
i been afraid to tell him
that i had told the police,

16:12.003 --> 16:15.373
and i didn't know
what to do.

16:15.373 --> 16:17.708
and i called kwasi.
did he know prince?

16:17.708 --> 16:22.596
uh-uh. i just wanted kwasi
to tell what happened.

16:22.596 --> 16:26.934
and he did it for me.
the other guy met you?

16:26.934 --> 16:32.640
he got out of his car
at fourth and "b,"
got in kwasi's backseat.

16:32.640 --> 16:38.479
kwasi said that i called 911
to take the drugs away, and that
that was the right thing to do.

16:38.479 --> 16:42.616
and that if he harmed me
over it, kwasi would call
the police himself.

16:43.117 --> 16:44.986
then he said that
he had been fronted...

16:44.986 --> 16:48.622
