but he just drove into
the front of the building.

17:07.558 --> 17:10.261
he must've
already been shot.

17:10.261 --> 17:15.766
then they came over
and shot the guy
in the backseat from close,

17:15.766 --> 17:19.103
then drove off.
but they didn't try
and shoot you.

17:19.103 --> 17:23.574
[ snorts ]
kwasi fell over me in the seat.

17:23.574 --> 17:25.409
i don't know
if they even saw me.

17:25.409 --> 17:28.829
