after the other one.

17:28.829 --> 17:32.033
- did you get any kind
  of look at them?
- not much.

17:32.033 --> 17:35.002
- jerome, what does that mean?
- i don't know how much
  a look i got.

17:35.002 --> 17:39.790
i got a look at 'em,
